<i>noun</i>: 이의 [이ː의/이ː이], 반론 [발ː론], 반대 [반ː대], 거역 [거ː역] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>이의 [이ː의/이ː이]</dt><br>
<dd>objection; disagreement; dissent</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 주장이나 결정 등에 대하여 가지는 다른 의견.</dd><br>
<dd>A different opinion held by one against a certain argument, decision, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>반론 [발ː론]</dt><br>
<dd>counterargument; objection</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람의 주장이나 의견에 반대하여 말함. 또는 그런 주장.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of saying something against someone's argument or opinion, or such an argument.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>반대 [반ː대]</dt><br>
<dd>1. opposite; contrary</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 것이 다른 것과 모양, 위치, 방향, 속성 등에서 완전히 다름.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which something is completely different from another thing in its shape, position, direction, quality, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>2. opposition; objection</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 행동이나 의견 등을 따르지 않고 거스름.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being against a certain behavior, opinion, etc., without following it.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>거역 [거ː역]</dt><br>
<dd>disobedience; insubordination; opposition; objection</dd><br>
<dd>윗사람의 뜻이나 명령 등을 따르지 않고 거스름.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of refusing to obey and acting against the will or command of a superior.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>